strings: <voice_0x010011C9><se_def>Daffodil: I am Leopoldo. It's dinner time! I'm leaving here
<voice_0x010011CA><se_def>The poem of Leopoldo: So "Okay, okay, okay!"
<voice_0x010011CB><se_def>Daffodil: wickedly! Did I do something that upset you? is pitiful!
<voice_0x010011CC><se_def>Daffodil: This is why you are the way you are!
<voice_0x010011CD><se_def>Daffodil: Thank you for what you do! happy sunday
<voice_0x010011CF><se_def>Daffodil: I think! As far as I know I went around the world about six months ago.
<voice_0x010011D0><se_def>Daffodil: But when I look at my clothes, I've traveled the world alone about six months ago.
<voice_0x010011D1><se_def>Daffodil: Yes, six months have passed. When he got here, he was tired, hungry and lost consciousness.
<voice_0x010011D3><se_def>Daffodil: He said he would let me work from home. Thank you very much!
<voice_0x010011D4><se_def>Daffodil: He can sometimes be very arrogant. but there's a good man inside
